<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0014892> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A muscle organ that consists of skeletal muscle tissue ensheathed in epimysium, that develops from myotome and that is innervated by some somatic motor neuron. Skeletal muscles are typically attached (via a tendon) to a bone but there are exceptions (e.g. intrinsic tongue muscles)." .
